# --- Personal operator docs & AI-assistant session files (2026-06-13) ---
# These were previously protected ONLY by .git/info/exclude, which is per-clone
# and never shared — so a fresh clone or a stray `git add -A` could track and
# publish them. Promoted here into the tracked .gitignore (same reasoning as the
# firefox_profile promotion above) so the protection is durable and travels with
# the repo. These are local operator context — NEVER for the public mirror.
# NOTE: the repo-root CLAUDE.md ignored here is Dean's PRIVATE operator file. If a
# public contributor-facing CLAUDE.md is ever wanted, it must live at a DIFFERENT
# path (e.g. docs/ARCHITECTURE.md) to avoid colliding with / leaking this one.
/CLAUDE.md
/GEMINI.md
/KNOWN_BUGS.md
/AGENT_SESSION_SAVE.md
/SESSION_HANDOFF*.md
*.code-workspace
/guaardvark_backup.json
/AGENTS.md
/PUSH_PREVIEW.md
docs/local-workspace-only/

# --- Non-essential / generated artifacts (untracked 2026-06-18, public-push sweep) ---
# Internal multi-agent audit/planning dumps (contain local absolute paths; not source)
regroup-reports/
# Per-machine build/runtime state, regenerated by start.sh / verify_gpu_stack.sh
frontend/.npm_stamp
data/gpu_stack_status.json
data/ollama-dropin.rendered.conf
